new tools for the expertise of its cars
in these days of bad weather , and of accidents , the car garages are not the only winners .
every day , thousands of cars that have suffered an accident are brought up in a garage , where an expert to assess the damage and the cost of repair .
every event is different , and the calculation of the cost of coins and the time of workforce can be a long and complex process .
calculating compensation to shoulder the cost of between 20,000 and 30,000 euros , including the documents and the workforce could take two or three hours .
on the other hand , with the assistance of the most recent computer tools , it would be a matter of minutes .
it is for this reason that nearly 100 % of the experts are using this type of system .
service providers and solutions for the evaluation of claims and maintenance devoted to the collection of information provided by the manufacturers , and then treat them and offer them to customers in the form of a useful tool .
in spain , audatex , leader of the north american solera , is the company ; 80 % of the assessments are made with its products .
other companies that compete in the field of tools to evaluate and to the development of information on the sector are gtmotive and eurotax .
's work with the information provided by the manufacturers is far from easy .
according to audatex eduardo velázquez , director of trade , the business in spain with 63 manufacturers and importers , and each one of them provides them with information in a different format .
in addition , the amount of data to deal with continues to grow , so that in the past five years , more than versions , and motorisations variants have been launched in the past 15 years .
when a new car fate in the market , the companies are at work .
it is a very difficult work , because you need to catalogue every thousand pieces of the vehicle and put his prize .
in addition , it puts a graphic image " intelligent " of each model on which we can click on the different parts of a car of tourism .
if it is a model sold in huge numbers , the work could be ready within a week if they are moving very quickly .
if it is a little car sold , it can take three or four months . at present , audatex has full information about 99,2 % of the cars sold in spain .
one of the most exclusive models , for example , they have information about the porsche , but not of the ferrari and lamborghini .
on the vehicles on the road , the number exceeds the 99 % .
to do the work of documentation and preparing the databases , audatex has eight centers spread all over the world in spain , france , germany , the united states , brazil , mexico , china and japan , and all of them are specialized in some brands .
the national headquarters is located , to alcobendas - madrid - .
there , more than 100 technicians or general of experts in mechanical work simultaneously on three computer screens .
audatex invest 90 million every year to make these databases .
every month , 2.5 million of data is stored , and the customers are actualisations every two days .
the drafting of the huge flow of information allows these companies to provide various uses , and to offer a variety of products .
the most frequent application for the repair and maintenance , but in different countries , there is also the tools for the management of the components of theft or to calculate the vénale or residual value of a car .
the only company that has a guide making inquiries about the value of the used car is eurotax in spain .
audatex does not propose in our countries , but it does so in the united states .
in view of the products offered by audatex , it is easy to get an idea of the type of support it can provide to workers in the sector .
this company offers 10 different tools , the flagship is audaplus evaluation standard , the solution of the fires , intended for the experts .
there are cars , bikes , industrial light and heavy vehicles .
in addition to the cost of coins , it takes into account the time to redress estimated by the manufacturer or the scales of paint .
this tool comes in accordance with its use , for every estimate .
the cost of 5.75 euros , the highest for customers who use it little , to a maximum 10 times per month .
then every insurance company , which has thousands of expertise , is negotiating a price with audatex .
other products , such as audavin , allow the full identification of a vehicle and machinery , with whom he is out of the assembly line , only through its chassis number .
audaglass focuses on the glass of cars , and audasubastas is an internet server opened to the business sector , which has enchérir on vehicles declared wrecks .
his office of statistics is very helpful to identify patterns , conducting tests géo-démographiques or knowledge of the current problems by mark or model .
it is possible to study , for example , how many models of a determined went in the garage to mark a failure or how many have suffered from serious claims for a certain period .
gt reason is the only spanish company that is devoted to the development of this type of tools .
it is selling , among other things , gt estimate , which is also meant to experts and provides digital images , as well as access to documents , official price and time of the manufacturer .
gt motivates is a company in the einsa group , founded in 1971 , as a provider of services and solutions evaluation of the claims , and devoiture outages or maintenance .
the assessment guide gt is a product of historical reference on the market .
the company is working with 24 , 000 users in garages , 3 100 experts , and 53 insurance companies .
its volume of business has grown at a rate of 20 percent per year over the past three years , and it has been a turnover of 10,8 million euros in 2008 .
at the beginning of last year , she has begun the process of globalization , with the introduction of an office in paris .
on its side , audatex was born in germany in 1966 , and is located in spain in 1979 .
according to the sources of the company , 62 percent of its turnover is being done in europe and the rest of the world , and the remaining 38 % in north and south america . it works with 900 insurance companies and 33 , 000 , of which 3,000 are garages in spain .
the turnover of the world solera - audatex , sidexa , informex abz , hollander and ims - s " amount to $ 557 million , more than 3.3 % in 2008 .
in our country , the company is set to receive 19.1 million euros , or 7.2 percent more than in the last year .
in 2005 , the group solera was quoted on the stock exchange to 1 billion dollars , today , its actions are estimated at a total of 2 , 400 million dollars .
for 2007 , it is a side on the new york stock exchange and is part of the standard & poor 's index of reference .
internet auction of cars , accidentées
in october last year , the group has bought autoonline solera , an internet platform to the sale of cars , motorcycles and of special vehicles victims .
the operation has involved a cost 59,5 millions of euros for 85 percent of the company 's capital , which could widen the next year to 15 % .
the aim of the acquisition was to deliver more added value services to its customers , with the possibility of international access to a huge market .
estimates of this service and is focused only on sale of workers in the sector , as the insurance companies , the experts , leasing companies , the garages , professional casses and vendors who must be registered before starting to carry out operations .
this platform was created in 1996 in germany and manages more than 650 , 000 operations in the whole of europe , including 500 000 in germany .
among its main markets are spain , france , greece , poland , and turkey .
there are currently more than 1500 sellers and 4,000 experts registered on the site .
it handles 3 , 000 announcements per day and on the spanish market , 100 new ads are published each day .
